{"tid":129690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新聞] 「女僕裝」餐廳不請男服務生 違性平遭罰","createTime":"2017-02-21T19:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T02:14:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6914d1f047aec31a001e9f1b8aaaaf02aad6553","tid":129690,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a4YJHZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa4YJHZb.jpg&h=28dca340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新北市板橋知名早午餐店因為不請男服務生，遭開罰15萬元。1名25歲的張姓男子說，他<br />\n日前打電話到這間餐廳應徵，但店家一聽到他是男生，就說「我們不要男的」，讓民眾覺<br />\n得遭性別歧視，難過又生氣，憤而向勞工局投訴。 <br />\n<br />\n女店員穿著可愛的女僕裝，吊帶格紋短裙，合身白色襯衫，再搭配黑絲襪，這是這間早午<br />\n餐店的特色之一，打出服務親切、餐點美味，在新北市板橋擁有2家店面，沒想到也因為<br />\n服裝要求，被求職者投訴性別歧視。 <br />\n<br />\n25歲的張先生因為性別是男生被餐廳拒絕，這讓他無法接受，氣得向勞工局投訴，勞工局<br />\n請男職員打電話測試，也得到相同結果。 <br />\n<br />\n《性別平等法》第7條清楚寫著，雇主對求職者之招募甄試進用，不得因性別或性傾向而<br />\n有差別待遇，唯一例外是工作性質僅適合特定性別者，不在此限，像是女性內衣店員或者<br />\n是男性貼身衣物模特兒等，才能限定男女生，但像餐廳服務生的工作，跟性別並無關聯，<br />\n僅僅只是因為男生不能穿女僕裝而拒絕招募男生，已經違法，業者不願接受採訪，只私下<br />\n透露，他們接受裁罰，也已經在訂製男服務生的衣服。(民視新聞周婉菱、姚家鼎新北市<br />\n報導) <br />\n<br />\n4.完整新聞連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/7WGK55\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F7WGK55&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7eed4f89\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/7WGK55</a>"},{"pid":"0fc967a08aa737d08a4a890b671bcde4a22c24dc","tid":129690,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T19:51:30.000Z","msg":"個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab7c051745b00e1f28eddeb2f956046b0f99fd7","tid":129690,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18799c111cb37138cea32fa6e227a5d98a26327b","tid":129690,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ca20a73a68bff7ffa66f51dccbf396981c82d9","tid":129690,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"係唔係要請個男仔返黎做偽娘女僕先得？<br />\n乜撚野條例黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b5a51d6a72d95a6399e6fc0501fa2d27823fef","tid":129690,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線"},{"pid":"d7f5fbefed7d407dba366f442981e08667f75ccf","tid":129690,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"267f17979bd7315d652e1c2234f0d5e89e63006c","tid":129690,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係要請個男仔返黎做偽娘女僕先得？<br />\n乜撚野條例黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係間餐廳自己on9講到咁白"},{"pid":"31ad8d0407f3571dd0a902897e505673fc9bfea4","tid":129690,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係唔係要請個男仔返黎做偽娘女僕先得？<br />\n乜撚野條例黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係間餐廳自己on9講到咁白</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都係講我地已經請左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會講到咁白"},{"pid":"b6d80549fbe5b016c9e64aba6893cf365b93d63a","tid":129690,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb5def9743edc0004b8eff322afb96be7d4e83a","tid":129690,"uid